# Example environment configuration for Nexa Images
#
# Set the base URL of your Zazzle store. When defined, the app will use this value to
# generate fallback buy URLs based on a product's slug. For example, if this is set
# to "https://www.zazzle.com.br/store/nexa_images" and a product has a slug "sticker-capivara-cozy",
# the fallback URL becomes "https://www.zazzle.com.br/store/nexa_images/sticker-capivara-cozy".
#
# IMPORTANT: Change this to your actual Zazzle store URL.
VITE_ZAZZLE_STORE_URL=https://www.zazzle.com.br/store/nexa_images
